# Strategy Execution Flow Diagram

```mermaid
flowchart TB
    Start([Trading Cycle Start]) --> Scan[Scan Active Symbols]

    Scan --> ZoneFoundation[Foundation: Supply & Demand Zones]
    ZoneFoundation --> |30% weight| ZoneScore[Zone Score]

    ZoneFoundation --> Trendline[Trendline Confluence]
    Trendline --> |20% weight| TrendlineScore[Trendline Score]

    Trendline --> PriceAction[Price Action Patterns]
    PriceAction --> |15% weight| PriceActionScore[Price Action Score]

    PriceAction --> Fibonacci[Fibonacci Levels]
    Fibonacci --> |12% weight| FibonacciScore[Fibonacci Score]

    Fibonacci --> Breakout[Breakout Retest Validation]
    Breakout --> |12% weight| BreakoutScore[Breakout Score]

    Breakout --> Structure[Market Structure BOS/CHoCH]
    Structure --> |8% weight| StructureScore[Structure Score]

    Structure --> RSI[RSI Analysis]
    RSI --> |10% weight| RSIScore[RSI Score]

    RSI --> MA[Moving Average Analysis]
    MA --> |8% weight| MAScore[MA Score]

    %% Aggregation
    MAScore --> Aggregate[SignalAggregator]
    ZoneScore --> Aggregate
    TrendlineScore --> Aggregate
    PriceActionScore --> Aggregate
    FibonacciScore --> Aggregate
    BreakoutScore --> Aggregate
    StructureScore --> Aggregate
    RSIScore --> Aggregate

    %% Confluence Calculation
    Aggregate --> Calculate{Total Score ≥ 65%?}

    Calculate --> |Yes| Generate[Generate Trading Signal]
    Calculate --> |No| Skip[Skip Symbol]

    %% Signal Validation
    Generate --> Validate[Enhanced Signal Validator]
    Validate --> |Valid| RiskCheck[Risk Management Check]
    Validate --> |Invalid| Skip

    %% Risk Check
    RiskCheck --> |Pass| Execute[Execute Trade]
    RiskCheck --> |Fail| Skip

    %% Execution
    Execute --> Order[Send Order to MT5]
    Order --> Track[Track Position]

    %% Skip Path
    Skip --> Next{More Symbols?}
    Track --> Next

    %% Loop
    Next --> |Yes| Scan
    Next --> |No| Wait[Wait for Next Cycle]
    Wait --> Start

    %% Styling
    classDef foundation fill:#ff6b6b,stroke:#c92a2a,color:#fff
    classDef enhancement fill:#4ecdc4,stroke:#0f9d8a,color:#fff
    classDef aggregator fill:#ffe66d,stroke:#f4a127,color:#000
    classDef decision fill:#a8dadc,stroke:#1d3557,color:#000
    classDef execution fill:#118ab2,stroke:#075f8a,color:#fff

    class ZoneFoundation foundation
    class Trendline,PriceAction,Fibonacci,Breakout,Structure,RSI,MA enhancement
    class Aggregate,Calculate aggregator
    class Validate,RiskCheck,Calculate decision
    class Execute,Order,Track execution
```

## Phase 2: Multi-Timeframe Analysis Flow

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    subgraph MTF["Multi-Timeframe Analysis"]
        direction TB
        M1[M1<br/>Scalping]
        M5[M5<br/>Scalping]
        M15[M15<br/>Scalping/Day]
        H1[H1<br/>Day Trading]
        H4[H4<br/>Swing]
        D1[D1<br/>Position]
        W1[W1<br/>Position]
    end

    subgraph Types["Trading Types"]
        Scalping[Scalping<br/>1-240 min]
        Day[Day Trading<br/>30-1440 min]
        Swing[Swing Trading<br/>1-7 days]
        Position[Position<br/>1-4 weeks]
    end

    %% Connections
    M1 & M5 & M15 --> Scalping
    M15 & H1 --> Day
    H4 & D1 --> Swing
    D1 & W1 --> Position

    %% Styling
    classDef timeframe fill:#f1f3f5,stroke:#495057,color:#000
    classDef tradingType fill:#e7f5ff,stroke:#1c7ed6,color:#000

    class M1,M5,M15,H1,H4,D1,W1 timeframe
    class Scalping,Day,Swing,Position tradingType
```

## Phase 3: Confluence Scoring Calculation

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start[Signal Received] --> F[Foundation Layer<br/>S&D Zones]

    F --> |Max 30 pts| F1{Zone Quality?}
    F1 --> |Fresh| F_Score[+30]
    F1 --> |Aging| F_Score2[+15]
    F1 --> |Weak| F_Score3[+5]

    F_Score & F_Score2 & F_Score3 --> T[Trendline Layer]
    F_Score3 --> T

    T --> |Max 20 pts| T1{Trendline Strength?}
    T1 --> |Strong 3+ touches| T_Score[+20]
    T1 --> |Moderate 2 touches| T_Score2[+10]
    T1 --> |None| T_Score3[+0]

    T_Score & T_Score2 & T_Score3 --> P[Price Action Layer]
    T_Score3 --> P

    P --> |Max 15 pts| P1{Pattern Quality?}
    P1 --> |Strong Engulfing| P_Score[+15]
    P1 --> |Pin Bar| P_Score2[+10]
    P1 --> |Weak| P_Score3[+5]

    P_Score & P_Score2 & P_Score3 --> Fib[Fibonacci Layer]
    P_Score3 --> Fib

    Fib --> |Max 12 pts| Fib1{Fibo Confluence?}
    Fib1 --> |At Key Level| Fib_Score[+12]
    Fib1 --> |Near Level| Fib_Score2[+6]
    Fib1 --> |None| Fib_Score3[+0]

    Fib_Score & Fib_Score2 & Fib_Score3 --> B[Breakout Layer]
    Fib_Score3 --> B

    B --> |Max 12 pts| B1{Breakout Valid?}
    B1 --> |Volume Confirm| B_Score[+12]
    B1 --> |Weak| B_Score2[+6]
    B1 --> |None| B_Score3[+0]

    B_Score & B_Score2 & B_Score3 --> S[Structure Layer]
    B_Score3 --> S

    S --> |Max 8 pts| S1{BOS/CHoCH Align?}
    S1 --> |Yes| S_Score[+8]
    S1 --> |No| S_Score2[+0]

    S_Score & S_Score2 --> R[RSI Layer]

    R --> |Max 10 pts| R1{RSI Confirm?}
    R1 --> |Oversold/Overbought| R_Score[+10]
    R1 --> |Divergence| R_Score2[+7]
    R1 --> |Neutral| R_Score3[+0]

    R_Score & R_Score2 & R_Score3 --> MA[MA Layer]

    MA --> |Max 8 pts| MA1{MA Align?}
    MA1 --> |Trend Confirm| MA_Score[+8]
    MA1 --> |Counter| MA_Score2[+0]

    MA_Score & MA_Score2 --> Total[Calculate Total]

    Total --> Check{Score ≥ 65?}
    Check --> |Yes| Pass[✅ Signal Valid]
    Check --> |No| Fail[❌ Signal Rejected]
```
